{"tid":2224723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青年被控非法集結 警否認現場講粗口 僅稱「手套你有冇」","createTime":"2020-09-30T17:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T18:53:15.000Z","uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a84510a6a2b29664650c4e4fd32a38a90894c966","tid":2224723,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T17:28:13.000Z","msg":"新天地外行人天橋上有人向警察掟磚，上橋掃蕩期間拘捕涉嫌掟磚的19歲青年。青年否認非法集結罪，事發近一年後，今在西九龍裁判法院受審。辯方質疑案中警署警長誤認被告是犯人，並指他的證供不盡不實，例如辯方指被告遭搜查時，有警察責罵「有手套，你老母」，警署警長起初卻否認；及後庭上播放傳媒直播片段聽到這句，他仍堅稱隱約聽到「手套，你有冇」，揚言「聽唔到你講嗰個粗俗嘅意思」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200930/INCYRE2OVVGIZLWYPWC3U7OBXQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3GJB2HgKXQaY4Ft7Zh4oRUXg1CGM9hq1jKE8jWDsaAbsjoWeTUHvyLVac\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200930%2FINCYRE2OVVGIZLWYPWC3U7OBXQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3GJB2HgKXQaY4Ft7Zh4oRUXg1CGM9hq1jKE8jWDsaAbsjoWeTUHvyLVac&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kynQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=72b533c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200930%2FINCYRE2OVVGIZLWYPWC3U7OBXQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3GJB2HgKXQaY4Ft7Zh4oRUXg1CGM9hq1jKE8jWDsaAbsjoWeTUHvyLVac&h=6c849ba5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200930/INCYRE2OVVGIZLWYPWC3U7OBXQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3GJB2HgKXQaY4Ft7Zh4oRUXg1CGM9hq1jKE8jWDsaAbsjoWeTUHvyLVac</a>"},{"pid":"4719a4495f3cd4d6c41b8e53ddb04bbe3f11a683","tid":2224723,"uid":301050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a84510a6a2b29664650c4e4fd32a38a90894c966","tid":2224723,"uid":